* Explicit Type\nCasting
** cast()
***_ Strict conversion
***_ Raises error on failure
***_ Use for strict validation
***_ Stops processing on invalid data
** try_cast()
***_ Returns NULL on failure
***_ No error raised
***_ Identify invalid values
***_ Filter / flag / quarantine
** Use Cases
*** cast
****_ Known-clean data
****_ Critical type conversions
*** try_cast
****_ Unknown/dirty data
****_ Validation & reporting
****_ Quarantine patterns
** Pattern
***_ try_cast in WHERE to filter valid
***_ Route invalids to quarantine
@endmindmap
